body:
Please provide details on what exactly you're doing. It seems like you're using `curl` but not specifying the file to download into, so it's dumping the contents to your screen.

```sh
curl "http://download.tensorflow.org/example_images/flower_photos.tgz" -o flower_photos.tgz
```

seems to work fine.
